{"tid":316834,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《真・三國無雙》拍真人電影，演員應點安排","createTime":"2017-07-11T04:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T14:39:23.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb935de35662d9a70bf50ef8d78ec088e21d4828","tid":316834,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"預計 2018 年上映的《真・三國無雙》真人電影版，現由 HMV 數碼中國主席蕭定一在個人微博透露，即將在 7 月 11 日開拍。<br />\n <br />\n作為亞洲地區的當紅 IP，《真・三國無雙》在 2016 年由中國 3D 數碼娛樂（現 HMV 數碼中國）發表翻拍真人電影，相傳不少一線男星都會參與拍攝，但至今尚未正式揭曉演員陣容。現在僅知周顯揚執導，杜致朗身兼編劇與監製。<br />\n <br />\n杜致朗過去作品包括《霍元甲》、《大追捕》、《蘇乞兒》，還曾參與《不能說的‧秘密》聯合編劇等。<br />\n <br />\n蕭定一在個人微博透露，拍三國演義的電影為從小夢想，為了想拍出新鮮感，四年前開始接觸光榮特庫摩遊戲，終於讓他取得《真・三國無雙》真人電影版翻拍權，欲拍一部大家從未看過的古裝片。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/32584/dynasty-warriors-live-action-film-start-shooting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F32584%2Fdynasty-warriors-live-action-film-start-shooting&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5335f204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/32584/dynasty-warriors-live-action-film-start-shooting</a><br />\n甄子丹-呂布<br />\n彭於晏-趙雲"},{"pid":"f339a06e1249071db02fa3a2d2cc8d6e32c67806","tid":316834,"uid":71229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"咁都可以開戲拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24d889f86e3e913b27cc51d2c620d1c7c409998","tid":316834,"uid":3067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:49:23.000Z","msg":"拍咩呀 拍割草？"},{"pid":"87b78187dde5f417cdac0c1904bfdec52dbdb3f6","tid":316834,"uid":68902,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"《真‧三國無雙》真人版電影將由香電影製作公司「中國 3D 數碼娛樂」負責改編與拍攝。演員將尋找中、港、台、日、韓等五國的演員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b672fb27e3efe42a880b5c5c4328ee3fd93ff5df","tid":316834,"uid":126902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"杜周兩個最出名果套殺人犯竟然唔提"},{"pid":"8db0f6cdde048d2ac3461e3ebe006f66844ea541","tid":316834,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:11:27.000Z","msg":"又杜緻朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab25c2f48cb5fc48daf3074d92b6fef5c4fd2d83","tid":316834,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"林敏聰<br />\n<br />\n禰衡"},{"pid":"ce13b37f27dae9684784d296da0d14c26b56702c","tid":316834,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"邊個做董卓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87b73a91602fadfb834c98e50f39bb9688d8c43","tid":316834,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>杜周兩個最出名果套殺人犯竟然唔提</blockquote><br />\n我又諗起你老婆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8305ef4bb4f87d6aaa1acf22af8c8ac363d2bc","tid":316834,"uid":68902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個做董卓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本何俊仁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d1fb30479d8b81d66b4b2a8250003ab910f626","tid":316834,"uid":894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"最衰隻game冇得用徐榮<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就可以徐榮飾演徐